            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " has a lot of potential and is far from a terrible game, but it sorely lacks polish. The seeds of an excellent retro video game are there, but the optimisation issues and frustrating design choices make it hard to see all of its good qualities. Make no mistake, they are there - it’s just hard to get to them without getting burned.",
